            <div id="about-square-30" class="square desktop color-change"></div>
            <p id="about-text-4" class="about-text button-text desktop">When you share your story</p>
            <div class="story-para">
                <p><span class="button-text">When you share your story</span> with another person, you are inviting them into your world, and in doing so, you build a larger community of people with shared worlds. That perspective is what creates connection– with individuals and with brands.</p>
                <p class="paragraph-spacing">When we first started Dirty Napkin in 2023, we hardly knew the difference between a font and a color. We genuinely thought that Comic Sans and blue were the same thing. Despite inexperience, we were eager and wanted to expand our design skills to the real world. Fast forward to modern day and we are a well-oiled machine.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="about-square-31" class="square desktop color-change"></div>
            <div id="about-square-32" class="square desktop color-change"></div>
            <p id="about-text-5" class="about-text button-text desktop">When you share your story</p>
        </section>
        <section class="what-we-do">
            <div class="content">
                <h3 id="about-text-6" class="about-text">At its core, Dirty Napkin is a two-pronged entity:</h3>
                <div class="mobile-squares-container">
                    <div class="square color-change"></div>
                    <div class="square color-change"></div>
                    <div class="square color-change"></div>
                </div>
                <p id="about-text-7" class="about-text">If you are currently pursuing your passion, we can design awesome graphics for you that boldly communicate who you are and draw in like-minded people.</p>
                <p id="about-text-8" class="about-text">If you haven’t yet started, let us be the inspiration. If a small team of four can create something that alters your world, you can do it too.</p>
                <div id="about-square-33" class="square desktop color-change"></div>
                <div id="about-square-34" class="square desktop color-change"></div>
