                    <h4>Evan Whitaker</h4>
                    <p>is our Designer and Brand Strategist. He is a figment of our imagination.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bio" id="dan">
                <img src="https://placehold.co/272x272.png" alt="Dan headshot" id="A3">
