            <div class="conclusion">
                <p>At the end of the day, our mission is to make you realize that the world is more interesting than you thought. And to make our moms proud. Those missions are very much based on the quality of the work and we are wholeheartedly committed to it; you better be too.</p>
                <p class="paragraph-spacing">If you are an independent creator, a heartfelt business, or our childhood crushes who are finally into us now that we’ve made it big and successful in the industry, we want to hear from you. </p>
